        "endTime": 6.416,
        "duration": 3.676,
        "sentenceIndex": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "Her heart raced as she picked it up.",
        "startTime": 6.416,
        "endTime": 9.006,
        "duration": 2.59,
        "sentenceIndex": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "It was a strange voice on the line.",
        "startTime": 9.006,
        "endTime": 11.525,
        "duration": 2.518,
        "sentenceIndex": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "They said, \"I’m sorry, but your husband was in an accident.\" Lisa's world stopped in that moment.",
        "startTime": 11.525,
        "endTime": 18.804,
        "duration": 7.279,
        "sentenceIndex": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "She felt cold all over.",
        "startTime": 18.804,
        "endTime": 20.459,
        "duration": 1.655,
        "sentenceIndex": 11
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 20.458912,
    "measuredDuration": 20.458912
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b2",
    "bundleIndex": 2,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Her husband was gone.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 1.62,
        "duration": 1.62,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "When Lisa reached the hospital, she felt scared and lost.",
        "startTime": 1.62,
        "endTime": 6.167,
        "duration": 4.547,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "The hallways were bright, but her heart felt heavy.",
        "startTime": 6.167,
        "endTime": 10.251,
        "duration": 4.084,
        "sentenceIndex": 14
      },
      {
        "text": "The nurse took her to a small room.",
        "startTime": 10.251,
        "endTime": 12.95,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "sentenceIndex": 15
      },
      {
        "text": "She saw doctors and nurses talking, but no one could help her.",
        "startTime": 12.95,
        "endTime": 17.883,
        "duration": 4.932,
        "sentenceIndex": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "They told her the news.",
        "startTime": 17.883,
        "endTime": 19.657,
        "duration": 1.774,
        "sentenceIndex": 17
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 19.657075,
    "measuredDuration": 19.657075
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b3",
    "bundleIndex": 3,
