        "endTime": 9.381,
        "duration": 3.33,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa wanted work, but it was hard to find a job.",
        "startTime": 9.381,
        "endTime": 12.85,
        "duration": 3.469,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "Every day, she looked in the newspaper and online.",
        "startTime": 12.85,
        "endTime": 16.457,
        "duration": 3.607,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "She took any job she could find and worked hard for money.",
        "startTime": 16.457,
        "endTime": 20.467,
        "duration": 4.01,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "The work is hard and makes her very tired.",
        "startTime": 20.467,
        "endTime": 23.371,
        "duration": 2.904,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 23.370862,
    "measuredDuration": 23.370862
  },
  {
